---
/**
 * VisuallyHidden — screen-reader-only text.
 *
 * Renders its children inside a `<span class="sr-only">` so assistive
 * technology announces the content while sighted users see nothing.
 *
 * Usage:
 *   <button>
 *     <svg aria-hidden="true">…</svg>
 *     <VisuallyHidden>Close</VisuallyHidden>
 *   </button>
 *
 * Relies on Tailwind's built-in `.sr-only` utility.
 */
---
<span class="sr-only"><slot /></span>
